    Whitfield, J. D. ; Biamonte, J. ; Aspuru-Guzik, A. Simulation of electronic structure Hamiltonians using quantum computers . Mol. Phys. 2011 , 109 , 735 – 750 , DOI: 10.1080/00268976.2011.552441
