        Tranter, A. ; Sofia, S. ; Seeley, J. ; Kaicher, M. ; McClean, J. ; Babbush, R. ; Coveney, P. V. ; Mintert, F. ; Wilhelm, F. ; Love, P. J. The Bravyi-Kitaev transformation: Properties and applications . Int. J. Quantum Chem. 2015 , 115 , 1431 , DOI: 10.1002/qua.24969
